Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:10.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,在开始之前，还要非常感谢 Expo 和 Crab Nebula 对 \N {\rENG} Before getting into it, also a big thank you to Expo and Crab Nebula for
