Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我开始思考，肯定有某种方法可以将这些数据 \N {\rENG} And so I started thinking, surely there's some way to get this data
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:26.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,从网络传输到计算机。 \N {\rENG} from the network down to the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这很有趣。 \N {\rENG} And it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:31.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道，Johannes，你和我最初是通过 Prisma \N {\rENG} You know, Johannes, you and I met originally through Prisma
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,和 GraphQL 以及数据库模式和诸如此类的东西认识的。 我 \N {\rENG} and GraphQL and database schemas and those kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:36.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,总是觉得这是一个非常相邻的问题，从 \N {\rENG} And this always struck me as a really adjacent problem, which is
