Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,当前的最佳实践或我们构建事物的不同方式是什么？ \N {\rENG} And what are the current best practices or different way how we can architect things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的。 \N {\rENG} Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,再说一遍，我喜欢将其锚定在，我们是如何到达这里的？ \N {\rENG} And again, I like anchoring this in , how did we get here?
