Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,您可以用Excel 文件向某人发送电子邮件，对吧？ \N {\rENG} You can email somebody in Excel file, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们有点明白了，就像，然后你就得到了。 \N {\rENG} We kind of get that, like, then you have it.
