Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:01.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以下载这些播放列表并在设备上兑现它们。 \N {\rENG} I could download those playlists and just cash them on the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:03.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就像你所说的一种谦虚的事情 \N {\rENG} And so that's like a kind of a modest thing you were
