Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,那行得通。 \N {\rENG} That just works.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,凉爽的。 \N {\rENG} Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们将缓存所有内容。 \N {\rENG} We'll cache everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:17.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,问题是我们仍然希望能够在离线时工作。 \N {\rENG} The problem is that we also still want to be able to work when we're offline.
