Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们的租户之一是，您永远不应该被阻止做您想做的事情。 \N {\rENG} one our tenants is you should never, ever be stopped from doing what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:28.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,由于另一台计算机的可用性或缺乏可用性。 \N {\rENG} By the availability or lack of availability of another computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:32.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想说，这也许也是你可以划清界限的地方。 \N {\rENG} And I would say this is maybe also where you can draw a line between.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:36.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前，还不是本地优先的软件， \N {\rENG} Current, not yet local-first software that's not entirely useless in an
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果它缓存了很多东西，那么至少在离线场景下我还可以阅读它。 \N {\rENG} offline scenario if it caches things a lot, so at least I can read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:45.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,但从那时起，它仍然允许您 \N {\rENG} But to go from there to that, it allows you to still do
