Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,乐观一样 \N {\rENG} optimistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,。 \N {\rENG} of caching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的，正是如此。 \N {\rENG} yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,不仅如此，而且，思考起来很复杂，对吧？ \N {\rENG} And it's not only that, but, like, it's just complicated to think about, right?
