Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,发布请求失败。 \N {\rENG} post request failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:16.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在我们已经告诉用户它有效了。 \N {\rENG} now we've already told the user that it works.
