Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:55.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,登机前将其缓存，以便可以离线使用。 \N {\rENG} it before you got on the plane so that it would be available offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后您在航班上编辑文档，然后着陆并上 \N {\rENG} And then you edit the document on the flight and then you land and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:01.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,线，它会说，我们很抱歉，当您离线时，此文档已更改 \N {\rENG} you come online and it says, we're sorry, this document has changed
