Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:10.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们现在正在将您重置为云状态，然后您的所有数据都会消失。 \N {\rENG} We're now resetting you to the cloud state and then all your data is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:14.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这种事只发生在我身上一两次，但是伙计，这很痛苦。 \N {\rENG} That's only happened to me once or twice, but man, that hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:19.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们所做的是，我们可以，你知道，如果只是你再次工作， \N {\rENG} What we do is we can, you know, if it's just you working again, there's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里真的没有任何问题，对吧？ \N {\rENG} not really any problem here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像我可以编辑数据一样。 然后 \N {\rENG} Like I can edit the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,当我上线时，我们就上传它。 \N {\rENG} And then just when I come online, we upload it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:27.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,真正的挑战是，如果您有两个不同的东西，编辑 \N {\rENG} The real challenge is if you have two different things, editing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:30.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,数据，然后需要合并它们的更改，对吧？ \N {\rENG} the data, and then you need to merge their changes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:34.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像我在播放列表中添加了一首曲目一样。 \N {\rENG} So like I added a track to the playlist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:38.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且，您知道，Spotify在播放列表中添加了一首曲目。 \N {\rENG} And, you know, Spotify added a track to the playlist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:40.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧，现在我们有冲突了。 \N {\rENG} Okay now we have a conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,冲突是我们将在这里使用的技术术语。 这 \N {\rENG} Conflict is the technical term we're going to use here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是困难的事情。 多年来， \N {\rENG} And so that's the hard thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:46.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,许多不同的系统以不同的方式解决了这个问题 \N {\rENG} And lots of different systems have approached this in different
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,，对吗？ \N {\rENG} ways over the years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:51.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像，Git 使您能够合并冲突，只要您 \N {\rENG} Like, Git gives you the ability to merge conflicts as long as you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:57.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,没有对同一文件或文件中的同一行进行编辑，对吧？ \N {\rENG} don't have edits to the same file or the same line in the file, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:01.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,CouchDB 和 PouchDB，你知道，他们使用所谓的最后写入者获胜。 \N {\rENG} CouchDB and PouchDB, you know, they use what's called last writer wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以无论哪个。 \N {\rENG} And so it's whichever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道，所有系统都同意，无论最后一个是哪一个， \N {\rENG} The, you know, all the systems agree that whichever the last one was will
