Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧，现在我们开始讨论有趣的分布式 \N {\rENG} Okay, now we start to get into, like, interesting distributed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:15.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,系统问题，因为你不能相信计算机上的时钟。 \N {\rENG} systems questions because you can't trust the clocks on the computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:18.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,那么，这是服务器的最后一个1吗？ \N {\rENG} So, is it the last 1 to the server?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:20.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,是否必须有一个中央服务器来决定？ 约翰内斯， \N {\rENG} Does there have to be a central server that decides?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:22.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可以摆脱那个中央服务器吗？ \N {\rENG} Can we get rid of that central server, Johannes?
