Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,剧透！ \N {\rENG} spoiler!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:25.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可以！ \N {\rENG} Yes, we can!
