Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:28.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们稍后再讨论这个问题。 \N {\rENG} We'll come back to that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就说得通了。 \N {\rENG} That makes sense.
