Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:06.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,因此，我们希望将您本地设备中的状态同步 \N {\rENG} So we want to synchronize the state that you have in your local device
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:09.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,到其他计算机，无论是云中的服务器还是与 \N {\rENG} to other computers, whether that servers in the cloud or other people
